name: Vertical distribution of the free-living Plathelminthes (Turbellaria) from the sandy beaches of the Belgian coast in 1985 and 1986
description: Density and biomass of meiofauna for 6 sandy beaches(Knokke,Mariakerke, Oostende, Heist, Bredene,Zwin) along the Belgian coast sampled between April 1985 andMay 1986. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Jouk, P. (1992). Studie naar de ecologie van de vrijlevende Plathelminthes (Turbellaria) van de zandstranden van de Belgische kust. PhDThesis. Limburgs Universitair Centrum: Diepenbeek. 2 volumespp.
